<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Submission Status Update</title>
  <style>
    /* Base styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #171717, #2d2d2d);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .logo {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      border-left: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      border-right: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #22c55e;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .divider {
      border-top: 3px solid #22c55e;
      margin: 10px 0;
      width: 50px;
    }
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .status-submitted {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .status-under_review {
      background-color: #eff6ff;
      color: #1e40af;
    }
    .status-revisions_required {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      color: #9a3412;
    }
    .status-accepted {
      background-color: #ecfdf5;
      color: #065f46;
    }
    .status-rejected {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      color: #991b1b;
    }
    .comments-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">Africa Journal</span><br>
        <span style="font-size: 16px;">of Social Work and Social Policy</span>
      </div>
      <div class="divider" style="margin: 15px auto;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Submission Status Update</h2>
      
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      
      <p>We're writing to inform you that the status of your submission titled <strong>"{{submissionTitle}}"</strong> has been updated.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <p>The status has been changed to:</p>
        <div class="status-badge status-{{newStatus}}">
          {{#if_eq newStatus "submitted"}}Submitted{{/if_eq}}
          {{#if_eq newStatus "under_review"}}Under Review{{/if_eq}}
          {{#if_eq newStatus "revisions_required"}}Revisions Required{{/if_eq}}
          {{#if_eq newStatus "accepted"}}Accepted{{/if_eq}}
          {{#if_eq newStatus "rejected"}}Rejected{{/if_eq}}
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {{#if comments}}
      <div class="comments-box">
        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Editor Comments:</h4>
        <p style="white-space: pre-line;">{{comments}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      
      <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
      
      {{#if_eq newStatus "submitted"}}
        <p>Your submission has been received and will be reviewed by our editorial team. You'll receive another notification when your submission is assigned to reviewers.</p>
      {{/if_eq}}
      
      {{#if_eq newStatus "under_review"}}
        <p>Your submission has been assigned to reviewers. The review process typically takes 4-6 weeks. You'll be notified when the reviews are complete.</p>
      {{/if_eq}}
      
      {{#if_eq newStatus "revisions_required"}}
        <p>Based on the reviewer feedback, revisions are required before your submission can be considered for publication. Please review the comments and submit your revised manuscript through your author dashboard.</p>
      {{/if_eq}}
      
      {{#if_eq newStatus "accepted"}}
        <p>Congratulations! Your submission has been accepted for publication. Our editorial team will contact you with further details about the publication process.</p>
      {{/if_eq}}
      
      {{#if_eq newStatus "rejected"}}
        <p>We regret to inform you that your submission has not been accepted for publication. Please review the reviewer comments for feedback. We encourage you to refine your work based on this feedback for future submissions.</p>
      {{/if_eq}}
      
      <a href="https://africajournal.org/author/dashboard" class="button">View Your Submission</a>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to <a href="https://africajournal.org/contact" style="color: #22c55e; text-decoration: none;">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{current_year}} Africa Journal of Social Work and Social Policy</p>
      <p>East Africa Social Work Regional Resource Centre</p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://africajournal.org/privacy" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="https://africajournal.org/unsubscribe" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">Unsubscribe</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
